title: TV | Duck Quacks Don't Echo
text: Final episode in the latest series of this comedy panel show which sees Lee Mack and his guests attempt to find the answers to all manner of questions, from random trivia to the downright daft. Joining them tonight will be Episodes star Stephen Mangan, Great British Bake Off co-host Sue Perkins and comedian Romesh Ranganathan.
